# QR Studio - TON Connect Manifest

{
  "url": "https://your-domain.com",
  "name": "QR Studio",
  "iconUrl": "https://your-domain.com/icon.png",
  "termsOfUseUrl": "https://your-domain.com/terms",
  "privacyPolicyUrl": "https://your-domain.com/privacy"
}

## Instructions

1. Replace `your-domain.com` with your actual domain
2. Create a 512x512 PNG icon
3. Upload this file as `tonconnect-manifest.json` to your domain root
4. Set `VITE_TON_CONNECT_MANIFEST` to the full URL

## Environment Variables

```bash
VITE_BOT_USERNAME=your_bot_username
VITE_STRIPE_PAYMENT_LINK=https://buy.stripe.com/...
VITE_TON_CONNECT_MANIFEST=https://your-domain.com/tonconnect-manifest.json
VITE_TON_WALLET_ADDRESS=YOUR_TON_WALLET_ADDRESS
```
